                        <note rend="inline" type="source">817.1051/407: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Hanna</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-07-18T19:00:00-04:00">July 18, 1930—7
                                p.m.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>68. Your despatch No. 72, June 26. Please continue your discussions and
